sequenceDiagram
    participant Student as Frontend (Student)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant LS as Lesson Service
    participant RED as Redis Cache
    participant AI as Groq (Llama 3 API)

    Student->>GW: POST /api/lesson/ai-tutor/ask
    GW->>LS: Forward Request
    LS->>RED: Check for Cached Response
    
    alt Cache Hit
        RED-->>LS: Return Cached AI Text
    else Cache Miss
        LS->>AI: Generate Explanation (Prompt Context)
        AI-->>LS: AI Response Content
        LS->>RED: Store Response (TTL 1 Hour)
    end
    
    LS-->>Student: Return Markdown Explanation
